parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to the non-deployment of airbags in the event of a crash, increasing the risk of injury or fatality.

the passenger airbag light does not recognize a passenger
the airbag light stays on after multiple ignition off-on cycles.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the valve cover gasket can cause oil to leak onto the alternator, leading to electrical issues, alternator failure, and potentially a fire hazard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel sensor can cause the fuel gauge to malfunction, leading to inaccurate fuel readings, and potentially leaving the driver stranded.
